</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/5845/for_window-minimum-size/?comment=5846#comment-5846</link><description>There's no way to do this with i3 at the moment. Your only chance would be to write an IPC script.</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2015 13:17:21 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/5845/for_window-minimum-size/?comment=5846#comment-5846</guid></item><item><title>Answer by Adaephon for &lt;p&gt;Hi,
