&lt;p&gt;However this does not work.&lt;/p&gt;
 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/5845/for_window-minimum-size/?answer=5847#post-id-5847</link><description>`floating_minimum_size` and `floating_maximum_size` are [*configuration options*](http://i3wm.org/docs/userguide.html#configuring). But `for_window` (which is an option itself) expects a [*command*](http://i3wm.org/docs/userguide.html#_list_of_commands) after the criteria. </description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2015 13:24:23 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/5845/for_window-minimum-size/?answer=5847#post-id-5847</guid></item></channel></rss>